channel.title: Why wont my server work?,
channel.description:

my port = 43594 and it only lets me on my server if i do 0.0.0.0 which is a localhost and ive used upto 3-4 source still doesent work,
could anyone please help,???

item.title: Why wont my server work?,

item.description:

[quote=“1337sim, post:2, topic:246132”]That’s 'cause you didn’t PF (portforward) so Type your username and password, leave the server’s IP and keep Port at 43594.

Just keep server IP blank then you’ll can play, but if you want the others to play you’ll need to PF[/quote]

doesent work, =[
